MatchMind AI – Smart Football Commentator

MatchMind AI is an AI-powered football commentator that analyzes match data, predicts results using XGBoost, and generates real-time audio commentary in multiple styles (analytical, dramatic, or energetic).
It offers a fully interactive Streamlit interface where users can explore match stats, simulated player performance, and receive smart tactical suggestions.

Features:
 • AI-based match result prediction (XGBoost)
 • Custom voice commentary using Google Text-to-Speech (gTTS)
 • Interactive UI built with Streamlit
 • Real-time event timeline and smart tactical advice
 • Designed UI mockups with Figma

Tech Stack:

Python, XGBoost, Pandas, gTTS, Streamlit, Figma, Excel
